EN: The boss knocked the table hard to make everyone quiet down.

ZH: 他使劲拍打着自己的肩膀，试图唤醒疲倦的身体。
EN: He slapped his shoulders hard, trying to wake up his tired body.

ZH: 学生们使劲拧动着笔盖，终于打开了它。
EN: The students twisted the pen cap hard and finally opened it.

